{"tid":2317622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【八仙嶺山火無人記得？】無視山火風險，缺德行山客亂彈煙灰","createTime":"2020-12-08T17:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T19:01:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d46a749dc77875187713e5cc7b8d3571875f70b","tid":2317622,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T17:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SWE1U1uPungrZO0lQp9Raw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS41Mzg0NjE1Mzg0NjE1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/5KMfD0oykVXHCi5p7I_icA--~B/aD01NTc7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/19d12c23c45263d101b6996e31d63d54\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSWE1U1uPungrZO0lQp9Raw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS41Mzg0NjE1Mzg0NjE1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5KMfD0oykVXHCi5p7I_icA--~B%2FaD01NTc7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F19d12c23c45263d101b6996e31d63d54&h=3f0d59b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫情下不少運動場所被封閉，行山便成市民的假日活動之一。不過行山客數目增加，質素便反而下降。近日有人被拍攝到在山上吸煙及亂彈煙灰，令其他行山客髮指，直斥其行為自私。<br />\n<br />\n網民Leonardo Deliromi前日(6日)在Facebook群組「香港行山路綫及資訊谷」分享登大帽山時的見聞，拍攝到有數名穿着日常裝束的年輕人行山，期間竟然站在茂密的草地上吸煙。發文者指，「一身名牌咁行山，擺明係跟風去打卡。仲要喺度食煙，煙灰隨地扔」。<br />\n<br />\n網民不斷批評相中行山客缺德，指其亂彈煙灰會「害己害人」，「如果因為煙頭而起山火點算」，又直指若有更多同樣行為，甚至可能造成「八仙嶺山火2.0」。亦有網民指「着返件行山衫先上山啦」，「一身名牌打卡唔係問題，山上食煙真係罪大惡極」。<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說：<br />\n<br />\nChris Chan：行山食煙，不知所謂，又強迫人食二手煙，又會增加山火可能性<br />\n<br />\nYiu Cheuk Chucky：佢哋當旺角行街咩着到咁樣行山<br />\n<br />\nWaiwai Lam：整熄啲煙頭先好走呀！我唔想再見到八仙嶺事件！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/網民熱話-無視山火風險-缺德行山客亂彈煙灰被鬧爆-092706754.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E5%B1%B1%E7%81%AB%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-%E7%BC%BA%E5%BE%B7%E8%A1%8C%E5%B1%B1%E5%AE%A2%E4%BA%82%E5%BD%88%E7%85%99%E7%81%B0%E8%A2%AB%E9%AC%A7%E7%88%86-092706754.html&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=192e89d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/網民熱話-無視山火風險-缺德行山客亂彈煙灰被鬧爆-092706754.html</a>"},{"pid":"c2b8cdb7618f48c3ef09d66d98205a97e4a3b6af","tid":2317622,"uid":59976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T17:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c6H64h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc6H64h.gif&h=33f12fe3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01066c193a9e99c654662d7c737c2ddc78797913","tid":2317622,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T19:01:49.000Z","msg":"剩係記得有條放火賤種害撚死人仲要拎埋傑青<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}